title: Obanor announces decision to return to Tech - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Obanor announces decision to return to Tech - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Kevin Obanor has announced his decision to return to Texas Tech and play another collegiate season having already produced 1,676 points, 889 rebounds and 35 double-doubles in his career.
